title: TTG Asia wishes everyone a Selamat Hari Raya Aidilfitri!
text:
TTG Asia wishes everyone a Selamat Hari Raya Aidilfitri! Singapore, July 16, 2015 
TTG Asia e-Daily will be taking a break for the public holiday on Friday, July 17. 

News will resume on July 20. 

Selamat Hari Raya Aidilfitri to all readers!
